These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, punk, metal
1. the fan of metal is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | pop | punk | metal |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, dog, cat
1. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Pet   | goat | cat | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, helicopter, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Transport   | helicopter | motorbike | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, gardening, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | baking | gardening | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
