.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, musical, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | musical | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
